{"id":998828656,"lang":"cpp","lang_name":"C++","time":"1 month, 3 weeks","timestamp":1689802882,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"15 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/998828656/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Longest Substring Without Repeating Characters","memory":"8.2 MB","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    int lengthOfLongestSubstring(string s) {\n        unordered_map<char, int> index;\n        int len = 0; \n\n        for (int i = 0, j = 0; j < s.size(); j++) {\n            if (index.find(s[j]) != index.end() && index[s[j]] >= i) {\n                i = index[s[j]] + 1;\n            }\n            else {\n                len = max(len, j-i+1);\n            }\n            index[s[j]] = j;\n        }    \n        \n        return len;\n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"longest-substring-without-repeating-characters","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
